{"tid":1853813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【整合】全港武漢肺炎疫症地圖，已更新第11、12宗資料","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T07:28:56.000Z","uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80ff4ff3cacb1c6cc1066a0b4df2a5a126f31a87","tid":1853813,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:25:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1Of93eGij1-nezhqJ3G5Z49yVR0KzChk-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1Of93eGij1-nezhqJ3G5Z49yVR0KzChk-&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=2167237b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1Of93eGij1-nezhqJ3G5Z49yVR0KzChk-</a><br />\n<br />\n個案越來越多，係咪好似跟唔到邊度奶過嘢？<br />\n所以經多日整合，做咗個疫情地圖，跟進患者同疑似病例嘅所在地，同埋去過嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n全部資料有source及已FC<br />\n<br />\n地點危險程度分5級：<br />\n黑色：確診人士現在所在地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紅色：確診人士去過嘅地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色：疑似病例現在所在地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灰色：疑似病例去過嘅地方（即係直情無被檢測過的高危人士去過嘅地方）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍色：未來可能用於檢疫、隔離或處理屍體嘅地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683a4a1700eaccce28e6856500b14e7d101ff19a","tid":1853813,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span></span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一齊收港共支共皮</span><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點